title: Meetings Set to Give Information on Study in Ireland (University of Arkansas)
text: ( Source : University of Arkansas ) Photo Submitted Students visited schools and historic sites last year in Ireland . Students studying teacher education at the University of Arkansas are invited to attend one of three informational meetings
